articles.description: The Baltimore Ravens placed Nnamdi Madubuike, sidelined in Monday's loss to the Detroit Lions, on injured reserve Saturday, which creates more uncertainty about the Pro Bowl defensive tackle's neck injury, as the veteran will now miss at least four games.
